trans-unit.source: Provides data for a PropertyChanged event, which you must create.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder data for en hendelse PropertyChanged, som du må opprette.

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Classes within the <xref:System.Printing> namespace are not supported for use within a Windows service or ASP.NET application or service.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION]> Klasser i den <xref:System.Printing>navneområdet støttes ikke for bruk i en Windows ASP.NET-program eller tjeneste.</xref:System.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Attempting to use these classes from within one of these application types may produce unexpected problems, such as diminished service performance and run-time exceptions.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å bruke disse klassene fra i ett av disse programtyper kan føre til uventede problemer, for eksempel dårligere tjeneste ytelse og kjøretid unntak.

trans-unit.source: If you want to print from a Windows Forms application, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil skrive ut fra en Windows Forms-program, kan du se den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>navneområde.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The name of the property that changed.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på egenskapen som endres.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>.
trans-unit.target: Kall avhending når du er ferdig med <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Fjerningsmetoden forlater den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>i en ubrukelig tilstand.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> so that the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Etter å avhending, må du frigi alle referanser til den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>slik at saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minnet som den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>ble bruker.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid kall fjerne før du slipper siste referanse til <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using are not freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> object.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ressurser den bruker ikke frigjort før saneringsoppsamling kall den <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metoden for den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>objektet.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> </xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are used by the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs"> </xref> og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles av den <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the unnamed Boolean parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`Aktiverer den beskyttede `Dispose(Boolean)` metode med parameteren uten navn boolsk satt til `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with the parameter set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>aktiverer `Dispose` med parameteren som er angitt til `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the Boolean parameter is `true`, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs> references.
trans-unit.target: Når parameteren boolsk er `true`, denne metoden Frigjør alle ressurser holdes av administrerte objekter som denne <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>referanser.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjectPropertyChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden starter den `Dispose()` metode for hver referert objekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.target: Henter navnet på egenskapen som endres.
